(116, 'CSS Štýly #1 - Border', 'html-css.png', 'V dnešnom článku si rozoberieme CSS štýl BORDER', 'Určite ste sa už pri k&oacute;dovan&iacute; stretli s ohraničen&iacute;m, keď ste potrebovali ohraničiť nejak&yacute; obr&aacute;zok, či niekde pridať ohraničenie. Dnes si uk&aacute;žeme ak&eacute; typy ohraničenia m&ocirc;žu byť a uvedieme nejak&eacute; pr&iacute;klady :)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:18px"><strong>&quot;border-style&quot; hodnoty</strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px">dotted - vytvor&iacute; bodkovan&eacute; ohraničenie</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px">dashed- vytvor&iacute; preru&scaron;ovan&eacute; ohraničenie</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px">solid - vytvor&iacute; pln&eacute; ohraničenie</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px">double - vytvor&iacute; dvojit&eacute; ohraničenie</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px">groove - vytvor&iacute; 3D ohraničenie</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px">ridge - vytvor&iacute; 3D vyv&yacute;&scaron;en&eacute; ohraničenie</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px">inset - vytvor&iacute; 3D vn&uacute;torn&eacute; ohraničenie</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size:12px">outset - vytvor&iacute; 3D vonkaj&scaron;ie ohraničenie</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="font-size:18px"><strong>&quot;border-width&quot; hodnoty</strong></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\nPr&iacute;klad na hodnoty pre<em> border-width</em>\r\n\r\n<div class="box"><strong>p.one {</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; border-style:solid;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; border-width:5px;<br />\r\n<strong>}<br />\r\np.two {</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; border-style:solid;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; border-width:medium;<br />\r\n<strong>}</strong></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:18px"><strong>&quot;border-color&quot; hodnoty</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>n&aacute;zov farby - zadať n&aacute;zov farby v anglickom jazyku, napr&iacute;klad &quot;red&quot;</li>\r\n	<li>RGB - zadať RGB hodnotu danej farby, napr&iacute;klad &quot;rgb(255,0,0)&quot;</li>\r\n	<li>Hex - zadať hex hodnotu farby, napr&iacute;klad &quot;#ff0000&quot;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPr&iacute;klad na hodnoty pre<em> border-width</em>\r\n\r\n<div class="box"><strong>p.one {</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; border-style:solid;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; border-color:red;<br />\r\n<strong>}<br />\r\np.two {</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; border-style:solid;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; border-color:#98bf21; <strong>}</strong></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-size:18px"><strong>Individu&aacute;lne strany</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<div class="box"><strong>p {</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; border-top-style:dotted;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; border-right-style:solid;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; border-bottom-style:dotted;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; border-left-style:solid;<br />\r\n<strong>}</strong></div>\r\n', '3', '1', '1375389069', 816, 'css, styly, 1, border', '0', 14),
(117, 'Android hry #7 [Tiny Thief]', '689tinythief.png', 'Ďalšia podarená hra od Fínskych vývojárov Rovio. Ale tentokrát to bola len skupina z tejto firmy pod menom Rovio Stars, no hra je po grafickej stránke a po stránke hrateľnosti perfektným titulom. Zabite nudu s touto logickou puzzle hrou. ', '<img alt="" class="boximg" src="https://lh5.ggpht.com/ybgVzpvLSfZLbTmSld-_6nBup4o8SNAlZ5ATTKQHWBMVcE6NlOe_4vSS2taI2UbK_Nw=h900-rw" style="height:450px; width:600px" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nSkupinka v&yacute;voj&aacute;rov z Rovio (<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=Rovio+Stars+Ltd.">Rovio Stars Ltd.</a>)&nbsp;sa dala do kopy a vytvorili perfektn&uacute; logick&uacute; puzzle hru. Po sl&aacute;vnych tituloch ako <em>Angry Birds</em> a <em>Bad Piggies</em> prich&aacute;dza ďal&scaron;&iacute; pod menom <strong>&quot;Tiny Thief&quot;.</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<iframe align="middle" class="boximg" frameborder="0" height="315" scrolling="no" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/x-hV0RaqcGI" width="560"></iframe> &nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHra sa odohr&aacute;va v stredoveku, teda pri hradoch, mestečk&aacute;ch, hradn&yacute;ch dvoroch, pir&aacute;tskych lodiach atď. Hlavn&yacute; hrdina je Tiny, ktor&yacute; je hľadan&yacute;m zlodejom po celom kr&aacute;ľovstve. Pri tejto hre budete musieť často zapojiť logick&eacute; myslenie, či už na zdolanie levelu alebo na odhalenie <em>&quot;secretov&quot;&nbsp;</em>, ktor&eacute; s&uacute; v hre implementovan&eacute; vo forme ako napr. zat&uacute;lan&yacute; denn&iacute;k, zlat&aacute; koruna, zlat&eacute; jablko atď.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="https://lh6.ggpht.com/LzD-M_bAOF8dn_LeskDzJ7kL6PdueZt6UOP9ym9aW_Uh8p5tRM_FdcAWlUnRr2cJo8_j=h900-rw" style="height:450px; width:600px" /><img alt="" class="boximg" src="https://lh3.ggpht.com/rXvmlE2XwBvsfjzNHEmgV13tPjFAucKAyKuGH4lc0dVb-W74gsNxBK8XScf--Ihm6HHV=h900-rw" style="height:450px; width:600px" /><br />\r\nObčas v&aacute;m pom&ocirc;že zvierac&iacute; kamar&aacute;t fretka, no i ten je pri v&auml;č&scaron;ine levelov skryt&yacute; a ak chcete mať pln&yacute; z&aacute;sah 3 hviezdičkami mus&iacute;te sa posnažiť a pohľadať ho. Taktiež si mus&iacute;te d&aacute;vať pozor aby v&aacute;s neuvideli či už vojaci alebo va&scaron;i nepriatelia, inak v&aacute;m level začne odznova.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="https://lh3.ggpht.com/-wdzNeftR8oSnL9ksFTqKpZdWZo9FdMuF8uA5YPgcX4QllMTZpKmk5EapP0GFC4up-_m=h900-rw" style="height:450px; width:600px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="https://lh3.ggpht.com/Rks90zApkcr-hZzbaStpeqpq1M43KazEtb-p7nI2e0Xqky3-2Q6axAwoJ7tOOJuCe7o=h900-rw" style="height:450px; width:600px" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Technick&eacute; inform&aacute;cie:</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Potrebn&yacute; Android O/S: 2.3+</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Aktu&aacute;lna verzia: 1.0.0</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>V&yacute;voj&aacute;r:&nbsp;<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=Rovio+Stars+Ltd.">Rovio Stars Ltd.</a></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Cena: 0,89&euro;&nbsp;</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Odkazy:</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.roviostars.tinythief">Odkaz na Google play&nbsp;</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;', '10', '6', '1375458702', 780, 'android hry, android, apk games, android games, google play, tiny thief, rovio, logická hra, logická puzzle hra', '0', 3),
(118, 'Inšpirujme sa #10 - Typografia 2', '664inspiracia.png', 'Už desiaty diel inšpirácie. Tentokrát si znova ukážeme niečo z typografie. Pokochajte sa kreatívnymi nápadmi a možno si nejaký zoberiete aj vy.', 'In&scaron;pirujte sa pr&aacute;cami kreat&iacute;vnych grafikov. Typografia je naozaj kr&aacute;sna, keď m&aacute;te n&aacute;pady.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://imgs.abduzeedo.com/files/tutorials/Beautiful_Water_Effect_in_Photoshop/media_1375057957107.jpg" style="height:373px; width:600px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://24.media.tumblr.com/ddc5b54fb5de7a8b19aba78639d12673/tumblr_mq3cwkvoMC1ryq9ado1_1280.jpg" style="height:587px; width:586px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/vhMcFDKV.jpg" style="height:840px; width:600px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://25.media.tumblr.com/22108cfa9c2744efc8f4e10f0b72e0f0/tumblr_mqfcn6gklq1ryq9ado1_1280.jpg" style="height:842px; width:595px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://25.media.tumblr.com/50fbae7ce635fa6848d5a679a07cea47/tumblr_mqfg5pEMcX1ryq9ado1_500.jpg" style="height:392px; width:500px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://24.media.tumblr.com/073b7108718b3fce2728364d4c89213e/tumblr_mqcm9eR1y01ryq9ado1_1280.jpg" style="height:576px; width:576px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://25.media.tumblr.com/7d05770d2e98362783312ca965ad75f8/tumblr_mq368xEnBy1ryq9ado1_1280.jpg" style="height:450px; width:600px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://24.media.tumblr.com/4db77c9a4d9e96c32dd02040709f7f19/tumblr_mqr3e5Mrgn1ryq9ado1_1280.jpg" style="height:849px; width:600px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://24.media.tumblr.com/6ecd94f802992ccfea8832bfc4590435/tumblr_mqp9j1Il3p1ryq9ado1_1280.jpg" style="height:800px; width:600px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://24.media.tumblr.com/214059b1bc72fe5c2ab96cb5378c5a23/tumblr_mqi17iEkKc1ryq9ado1_1280.jpg" style="height:338px; width:600px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://31.media.tumblr.com/b8ce8d664ba8e1ab38ab9c9a977e47c1/tumblr_mqr5f6Vfs31ryq9ado1_1280.jpg" style="height:800px; width:600px" />', '22', '6', '1375524741', 593, 'inšpirujme sa, inšpirácia, typografia', '0', 2),
(119, 'CSS Štýly #2 - Background', 'html-css.png', 'V tomto článku si rozebereme další CSS vlastnost a tou je Background, neboli pozadí.', 'V minul&eacute;m čl&aacute;nku n&aacute;m felipe popsal CSS vlastnost <a href="http://www.desart.sk/clanok/116/css-styly-1-border">border</a>. V dne&scaron;n&iacute;m čl&aacute;nku si pop&iacute;&scaron;eme jednu z hlavn&iacute;ch vlastnost&iacute; a to background, neboli pozad&iacute;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Barva pozad&iacute;:</h3>\r\n<strong>background-color</strong><br />\r\n#000000 - Z&aacute;pis barvy v hexadecim&aacute;ln&iacute; soustavě.<br />\r\nblack - Z&aacute;pis barvy v anglick&eacute;m jazyce.<br />\r\nrgb(0,250,0) - Z&aacute;pis barvy pomoc&iacute; RGB.<br />\r\ntransparent - Průhledn&eacute; pozad&iacute;.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Z&aacute;pis:</strong>\r\n\r\n<div class="box">background-color: #000000;</div>\r\n​\r\n\r\n<h3>Obr&aacute;zek pozad&iacute;:</h3>\r\n<strong>background-image</strong><br />\r\nurl(&quot;cesta_k_obrazku.png&quot;)<br />\r\nnone - Bez pozad&iacute; (defaultn&iacute;)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Z&aacute;pis:</strong>\r\n\r\n<div class="box">background-image: url(cesta_k_obrazku.png);</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<h3>Pozice obr&aacute;zkov&eacute;ho pozad&iacute;:</h3>\r\n<strong>background-position</strong><br />\r\nObsahuje 2 hodnoty, posunut&iacute; v ose X a v ose Y.<br />\r\nOsa X&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>​left - Zarovn&aacute; obr&aacute;zek na levo v ose X.</li>\r\n	<li>center - Zarovn&aacute; obr&aacute;zek na střed v ose X.</li>\r\n	<li>right - Zarovn&aacute; obr&aacute;zek na pravo v ose X.</li>\r\n	<li>px</li>\r\n	<li>%</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOsa Y\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>top - Zarovn&aacute; obr&aacute;zek nahoru&nbsp;v ose Y.</li>\r\n	<li>center - Zarovn&aacute; obr&aacute;zek na střed v ose Y.</li>\r\n	<li>bottom - Zarovn&aacute; obr&aacute;zek do spodu v ose Y.</li>\r\n	<li>px</li>\r\n	<li>%</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Z&aacute;pis:</strong>\r\n\r\n<div class="box">background-position: center top;</div>\r\n<em>Zarovn&aacute; obr&aacute;zek na střed v ose X a nahoru v ose Y.</em><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Opakov&aacute;n&iacute; obr&aacute;zkov&eacute;ho pozad&iacute;:</h3>\r\n<strong>background-repeat</strong><br />\r\nrepeat - Opakov&aacute;n&iacute; pozad&iacute; jak v ose X, tak i v ose Y (defaultn&iacute;).<br />\r\nrepeat-x - Opakov&aacute;n&iacute; pozad&iacute; v ose X.<br />\r\nrepeat-y - Opakov&aacute;n&iacute; pozad&iacute; v ose Y.<br />\r\nno-repeat - Pozad&iacute; se neopakuje.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Z&aacute;pis:</strong>\r\n\r\n<div class="box">background-repeat: repeat-y;</div>\r\n​\r\n\r\n<h3>Rolov&aacute;n&iacute; (posouv&aacute;n&iacute;) obr&aacute;zkov&eacute;ho pozad&iacute;:</h3>\r\n<strong>background-attachment</strong><br />\r\nfixed - Pozad&iacute; je pevn&eacute;, drž&iacute; na jednom m&iacute;stě (defaultn&iacute;).<br />\r\nscroll - Pozad&iacute; se posouv&aacute; (scrolluje) se str&aacute;nkou.<br />\r\n​<br />\r\n<strong>Z&aacute;pis:</strong>\r\n\r\n<div class="box">background-attachment: scroll;</div>\r\n​\r\n\r\n<h3>Jednoř&aacute;dkov&yacute; z&aacute;pis:</h3>\r\n\r\n<div class="box">background: #000000 url(cesta_k_obrazku.png) top center repeat-y scroll;</div>\r\n', '3', '233', '1375563093', 773, 'css, styly, background, pozadí', '0', 14),
(121, 'Inšpirujme sa #11 - Super dizajny pre slidery', '664inspiracia.png', 'Slider - jedna z častí webu, ktorá ho robí živším a zaujímavejším. Teda, záleží na prevedení či grafickom alebo kóderskom. Nechajte sa inšpirovať od kreatívnych grafikov.', '<h3 style="color:#aaa; font-style:italic">Slider je veľmi d&ocirc;ležitou časťou webu po str&aacute;nke reprezentovania či informovania. Tieto slidre nesl&uacute;žia len pre premietanie obr&aacute;zkov, ale tiež ako v&scaron;eobecn&yacute; obsah webu a samotn&aacute; navig&aacute;cia webu. Preto je d&ocirc;ležit&eacute; ich prevedenie po grafickej str&aacute;nke a po str&aacute;nke programovania. Nechajte sa in&scaron;pirovať &scaron;ikovn&yacute;mi n&aacute;padmi ako oživiť web.</h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href="http://relogik.com/" style="color: rgb(39, 174, 96);" target="_blank">Relogik</a></h2>\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/RGjpB92H.png" style="height:286px; width:650px" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nOrigin&aacute;lny &scaron;t&yacute;l a prevedenie. Určite je to veľmi origin&aacute;lny slider.\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.webcontact.de/de/" style="color:#27ae60;" target="_blank">Webcontact</a></h2>\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/CTxQRXwy.png" style="height:289px; width:650px" /><br />\r\nSlider je zakomponovan&yacute; veľmi pekne ako pevn&aacute; s&uacute;časť webu. Jednoduch&eacute; premietanie obr&aacute;zku a textu je vhodne použit&eacute;.\r\n<h2><a href="http://bitfoundry.ca/" style="color:#27ae60;" target="_blank">Bitfoundry</a></h2>\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://webdesignledger.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/slider03.jpg" style="height:265px; width:580px" /><img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://webdesignledger.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/slider03a.jpg" style="height:258px; width:580px" /><br />\r\nKr&aacute;sny flat &scaron;t&yacute;l tejto str&aacute;nky je použit&yacute; aj v slideshowe, ktor&yacute; p&ocirc;sob&iacute; veľmi pekne. Web funguje na HTML5\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.maisengasse.at/" style="color:#27ae60;" target="_blank">Buro Maisengasse</a></h2>\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://webdesignledger.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/slider07.jpg" style="height:321px; width:580px" /><br />\r\nAsi najorigin&aacute;lnej&scaron;&iacute; typ slideru, ktor&yacute; n&aacute;&scaron; čl&aacute;nok obsahuje. Perfektn&eacute; prevedenia po oboch str&aacute;nkach. Je použit&yacute; aj jQ s veľmi pekn&yacute;m efektom pos&uacute;vania.\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.mathieuclauss.com/" style="color:#27ae60;" target="_blank">Mathieu Clauss</a></h2>\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://webdesignledger.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/slider08.jpg" style="height:365px; width:580px" /><br />\r\nĎal&scaron;ie pekn&eacute; prevedenia v HTML5. Kr&aacute;sny a čist&yacute; obr&aacute;zkov&yacute; slider, ktor&yacute; V&aacute;m uk&aacute;že &scaron;&iacute;pky až po nabehnut&iacute; my&scaron;ou a kr&uacute;žky v ľavom dolnom rohu V&aacute;m ukazuj&uacute; kde sa nach&aacute;dzate.\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.marcorotoli.com/" style="color:#27ae60;" target="_blank">Marco Rotoli</a></h2>\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://webdesignledger.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/slider14.jpg" style="height:368px; width:580px" /><br />\r\nĎal&scaron;&iacute; slider preveden&yacute; v HTML5 ukazuje v&scaron;etky pr&aacute;ce a projekty, ktor&eacute; vytvoril twnto naozaj &scaron;ikovn&yacute; grafik. Premietanie je vymyslen&eacute; veľmi origin&aacute;lne.\r\n<h2><a href="http://www.jdetraz.com/" style="color:#27ae60;" target="_blank">J&eacute;r&ocirc;me D&eacute;traz</a></h2>\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://webdesignledger.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/slider20.jpg" style="height:369px; width:580px" /><br />\r\nKr&aacute;sny dizajn s cool sliderom, ktor&yacute; V&aacute;s naviguje a zoznamuje V&aacute;s s autorom.\r\n<h2><a class="signUpNew" href="https://getcu3er.com/" rel="prettyPhoto" style="color:#27ae60;" target="_blank">CU3ER</a></h2>\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/zZRkPLC7.png" style="height:316px; width:650px" /><br />\r\nNo a nakoniec je tu neskutočn&yacute; 3D slider, ktor&yacute; m&aacute; ocenenie awwwwards! Tento skvel&yacute; slider si m&ocirc;žete zaobstarať na ich str&aacute;nke! Je vytvoren&yacute; v jQuery<span style="color:rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family:lucida grande,lucida sans unicode,arial,sans-serif">.</span>', '22', '6', '1375722353', 736, 'inšpirujme sa, inšpirácia, slider, dizajny sliderov, inšpirácia sliderov', '0', 2),
(122, 'Photoshop videonávod #2 - Trojuholníkový pixelový efekt', '730trojuholníkovypixelovýefekt.png', 'Po dlhom čase je tu znova videonávod, kde si ukážeme ako vytvoriť celkom pekný efekt, ktorý môže byť použitý ako pozadie. Jedná sa o tzv. "Trojuholníkový pixelový efekt".', '<div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<iframe class="boximg" frameborder="0" height="315" scrolling="no" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/ovBL5bSCrMc" width="560"></iframe></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Druh&yacute; viden&aacute;vod od Frodasa. Dnes V&aacute;m uk&aacute;žem ako si m&ocirc;žete &uacute;plne jednoducho vytvoriť veľmi zauj&iacute;mav&yacute; a v celku pekn&yacute; efekt na pozadie.</strong>\r\n\r\n<h1 style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:22px"><a href="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/PptCRdbj.png" style="color:#27ae60;">Použit&eacute; pozadie</a>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<a href="http://www.mediafire.com/?a9cu9omy9yj6ucf" style="color:#27ae60;">PSD. s&uacute;bor</a></span></h1>\r\n', '1', '6', '1376739443', 1099, 'videonávod, photoshop ,photoshop cs6, triangle pixelate effect', '0', 12),
(123, '[Adobe After Effects] Realistický výstrel zo zbrane', '94558282.png', 'V tomto článku si ukážeme ako vytvoriť realistický výstrel zo zbrane pomocov Adobe After Effects, pripravil som si pre vás aj pack muzzle flash-ov a zvukov zbraní.', '<p><img alt="" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/dQNhnBHL.png" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Niečo o muzzle flash ( efekt v&yacute;strelu zo zbrane )</strong><br />\r\nNa internete (youtube,vimeo,...) a vo filmoch sa m&ocirc;žete stretn&uacute;ť z dvoma (2) r&ocirc;znimy typmi v&yacute;strelu.<br />\r\nJeden je realistickej&scaron;&iacute; - vo filmoch a druh&yacute; menej re&aacute;lny - &quot;amat&eacute;rske vide&aacute;&quot; :D ... .<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Ak&eacute; s&uacute; rozdiely ?</strong><br />\r\nVľavo m&ocirc;žete vidieť fikt&iacute;vny v&yacute;strel z filmovej sc&eacute;ny a vpravo zas z videa na youtube.<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/prKRt4c8.png" style="height:228px; width:500px" /><br />\r\nNajčastej&scaron;ie chyby začiatočn&iacute;kov:<br />\r\n1. mzzle flash je pr&iacute;liž mal&yacute;<br />\r\n2. žiaden dym<br />\r\n3. žiadny sveteln&yacute; z&aacute;blesk po v&yacute;strele, viď. obr&aacute;zok hore ;)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>N&aacute;vod ako vytvoriť realistick&yacute; v&yacute;strel zo zbrane.</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nSamozrejme budete potrebovať aj nejak&yacute; ten dym, a v&yacute;strel,<br />\r\npreto som pre v&aacute;s vytvoril mal&yacute; pack na stiahnutie -&nbsp;<a href="http://adf.ly/TYzYT">http://adf.ly/TYzYT</a><br />\r\nTento pack obsahuje z&aacute;kladn&eacute; zvuky zbran&iacute; a v&yacute;streli spolu s dymom ktor&eacute; boli<br />\r\nnahran&eacute; a upraven&eacute; z re&aacute;lneho v&yacute;strelu.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Zač&iacute;name.</strong><br />\r\nNatočen&uacute; sc&eacute;nu v&yacute;strelu si presunieme do kompoz&iacute;cie.<br />\r\nDo tejto kompoz&iacute;cie prenesieme aj muzzle flash s packu, presunieme ho na spr&aacute;vne miesto,<br />\r\npopr&iacute;pade otoč&iacute;me pomocou rotation tool v panely n&aacute;strojov skratka &quot;W&quot; .<br />\r\n(pokial je muzzle flash na obr&aacute;ten&yacute; opačne, pomocov kl&aacute;vesi &quot;S&quot; scale si nadstav&iacute;te na z&aacute;porn&eacute; hodnoty)<br />\r\nNezabudnite tiež na časov&uacute; os, presunte muzzle flash presne do toho frame-u kedy sa v&yacute;strel zač&iacute;na.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/xWZJtBhm.png" style="height:426px; width:800px" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nV&yacute;strel m&aacute;me hotov&yacute;, a teras sveteln&yacute; z&aacute;blesk, duplikujeme si spodn&uacute; vrstvu a nadstav&iacute;me m&oacute;d na &quot;add&quot; .<br />\r\nV panely n&aacute;strojov si n&aacute;jdeme pen tool( kl&aacute;vesov&aacute; skratka &quot;G&quot; ) a označ&iacute;me si miesta kde chceme aby bolo vydieť zosvetlenie.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/MYNbdVG4.png" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/Z2d4mKbP.png" style="height:582px; width:800px" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nPotom si rozklikneme masky a nadstav&iacute;me si rozpt&iacute;lenie ( mask feather ) na hodnoty medzi 10 - 100 podľa toho ako v&aacute;m to zapasuje.<br />\r\nNezabudnite st&aacute;le dbať na re&aacute;lnosť preto nadstav&iacute;me masky bliž&scaron;ie k v&yacute;strelu opacity na vyž&scaron;iu hodnotu ako tie ktor&eacute; s&uacute; od v&yacute;strelu ďalej.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPosledn&aacute; vec ktor&uacute; e&scaron;te treba spraviť je nadstaviť z&aacute;blesk na dlh&scaron;iu dobu pretože oko moc z v&yacute;strelu na 1 frame nezachyt&iacute;.<br />\r\nSc&eacute;nku ktor&aacute; zobrazuje svetlo, teda z&aacute;blesk si nadstav&iacute;me 1 frame pred a 2 frame po v&yacute;strele.<br />\r\nNadstav&iacute;me kl&uacute;čov&eacute; sn&iacute;mky.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/kTQXRHJL.png" style="height:163px; width:800px" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nOpacity som použil najvac 60% ale z&aacute;lež&iacute; na tom ako to kde zapasuje.<br />\r\nPotom stač&iacute; už len vyrendrovať a je hotovo ;)<br />\r\nD&uacute;fam že sa v&aacute;m m&ocirc;j n&aacute;vod p&aacute;čil ak &aacute;no nezabudnite dať like :D<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Fin&aacute;lny efekt:</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/X4fWYxqk.gif" style="height:360px; width:360px" /></strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '13', '82', '1376474254', 1129, 'adobe after effects, realistický, výstrel, zo, zbrane', '0', 0),
(124, 'Android aplikácie - Nova Launcher, PlayerPro', '694android-150x150.jpg', 'Ďalší diel android aplikácií. Dnes vám ukážem šikovné "appky" pre upravenie prostredia a prehrávač na hudbu, ktorý obsahuje aj ekvalizér.', '<h2>&nbsp;Nova Launcher&nbsp;</h2>\r\nLauncher je jedna z vychyt&aacute;vok androidu. Pomocou tejto aplik&aacute;cie si m&ocirc;žete upraviť va&scaron;e prostredie, dom&aacute;cu obrazovku, ikony atď. S&uacute; k dizpoz&iacute;ci&iacute; dve verzie - platen&aacute; a neplaten&aacute;. Verzia PRIME m&aacute; viacej funkci&iacute; ale ja si mysl&iacute;m že stač&iacute; i verzia zdarma. Podporuje android 4.0 a vy&scaron;&scaron;&iacute;.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Veľkosť: 22k<br />\r\nMinim&aacute;lna verzia OS: 4.0+<br />\r\nGoogle play: </strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong style="font-size:12px"><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.teslacoilsw.launcher.prime" target="_blank">NOVA LAUNCHER PRIME</a>&nbsp;- 3&euro;</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.teslacoilsw.launcher" target="_blank">NOVA LAUNCHER</a>&nbsp;- ZDARMA</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;PlayerPro Prehr&aacute;vač Hudby</h2>\r\nPokročil&yacute; prehr&aacute;vač hudby a videa pre android 2.x zariadenia. PlayerPro sa vyznačuje pekn&yacute;m, r&yacute;chlym a intuit&iacute;vnym rozhran&iacute;m. Navy&scaron;e m&aacute;te na v&yacute;ber z viacer&yacute;ch bezplatn&yacute;ch pluginov ako: <strong>20+ skinov, DSP bal&iacute;ček, Widget bal&iacute;ček.</strong><br />\r\nT&aacute;to aplik&aacute;cia bola dosť dlh&uacute; dobu v top &quot;appk&aacute;ch&quot; pre hudbu a video. Odpor&uacute;čam, uľahčuje pr&iacute;stup.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Veľkosť: 4,9MB<br />\r\nMinim&aacute;lna verzia OS: 2.0+<br />\r\nGoogle play: <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tbig.playerpro" target="_blank">PLAYERPO</a><br />\r\nCena: 3,95&euro;</strong>', '10', '6', '1376046797', 847, 'android, android aplikácie, aplikácie, aplikácie na android, nova launcher, playerpro', '0', 15),
(125, 'Videoeditory #1 - Pinnacle Studio', '73512035.jpg', 'Jako první článek v novém seriály s názvem "Videoeditory" si představíme nejrozšířenější videoeditor od firmy Corel - Pinnacle Studio.', 'Pinnacle Studio je komerčně nej&uacute;spě&scaron;něj&scaron;&iacute; a nejroz&scaron;&iacute;řeněj&scaron;&iacute; videoeditor, kter&yacute; m&aacute; moment&aacute;lně nejnověj&scaron;&iacute; verzi, a to verzi s&nbsp;pořadov&yacute;m č&iacute;slem 16. Přechod na novou verze i chv&iacute;li trval, protože to pravděpodobně zdržela nov&aacute; kanadsk&aacute; firma Pinnacle Studia Corel, kter&aacute; zač&iacute;nala naplňovat svoji softwarovou sb&iacute;rku. Od poč&aacute;tku bylo jasn&eacute;, že firma Corel chce Pinnacle udržet jako separ&aacute;tn&iacute; divizi. Pro zaj&iacute;mavost je dobr&eacute; se i zm&iacute;nit, že b&yacute;val&eacute; firmě s&nbsp;n&aacute;zvem Avid, kter&aacute; vlastnila Pinnacle, trvalo &scaron;est let, než se zbavila nestability a z&nbsp;programu Pinnacle Studio udělala hit.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/wBxzkJWf.png" style="float:center" /><br />\r\nI po přechodu k&nbsp;jin&eacute; firmě program c&iacute;l&iacute; na průměrn&eacute;ho uživatele. Pracovn&iacute; plocha programu přehledn&aacute; a relativně nekomplikovan&aacute;. I když je rozhran&iacute; programu graficky podobn&eacute;, tak identick&eacute; nen&iacute; a znalosti z&nbsp;minul&yacute;ch verz&iacute; n&aacute;m moc nepomohou. Na rozd&iacute;l od konkurenčn&iacute;ho programu Adobe Premiere Elements je u Pinnacle Studia kladen vět&scaron;&iacute; důraz na klasick&eacute; videoeditace a důkladněj&scaron;&iacute; aplikace pro import, doladěn&iacute; a export souborů. Na spodn&iacute; straně programu najdeme časovou linku, u kter&eacute; z&iacute;sk&aacute;me př&iacute;stup ke klipům, přechodům, titulkům či zvukov&yacute;m efektům. Soubor si jako u vět&scaron;iny editorsk&yacute;ch programů přet&aacute;hneme do časov&eacute; linky a jen upravujeme, zkracujeme, stř&iacute;h&aacute;me, přid&aacute;v&aacute;me zvukovou stopu či jin&eacute; věci.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/BXxZzH6h.png" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n&bdquo;Zkr&aacute;tka pr&aacute;ce v&nbsp;Pinnacle Studiu nen&iacute; až tak těžk&aacute;. Na p&aacute;r pohledů to vypad&aacute; jako složit&aacute; věc, ale určitě nen&iacute;. Po stažen&iacute; tohoto programu jsem se děsil, ale poř&aacute;dně jsem si to prohl&iacute;dl a chv&iacute;lemi mi to připadala jako klasick&yacute; z&aacute;kladn&iacute; program od Windows &ndash; Amat&eacute;rsk&yacute; Movie Maker.&nbsp; Za p&aacute;r dn&iacute; jsem se už radoval, že jsem udělal sv&eacute; prvn&iacute; video v&nbsp;tomto programu, kter&eacute; byůo použito při obhajobě ve &scaron;kole. V&nbsp;tomto programu jde zkr&aacute;tka skoro v&scaron;echno a tak&eacute; si mysl&iacute;m, že to bude podobn&eacute; programu Sony Vegas, o kter&eacute;m jsem tak&eacute; uvažoval. Na z&aacute;věr bych V&aacute;m tedy tento program Pinnacle Studio chtěl doporučit a ř&iacute;ct, že to nen&iacute; vůbec nic těžk&eacute;ho.&ldquo;', '8', '35', '1376130910', 666, 'pinnacle studio, video, rezence', '0', 13),
(126, 'Videoeditory #2 - AVS', '78317435.jpg', 'V dalším článku v rubrice "Videoeditory" si představíme další program, přes který se dají upravovat a dělat videa - AVS Video', 'AVS Video Editor je střihov&yacute; program, zaměřen&yacute; hlavně na střih dom&aacute;c&iacute;ho videa. Tomu odpov&iacute;d&aacute; i jednoduch&eacute; prostřed&iacute; a snadn&aacute; obsluha. Tento program zvl&aacute;dne zpracovat v&scaron;echny nejnověj&scaron;&iacute; form&aacute;ty videa, obsahuje množstv&iacute; filtrů a přechodů, nechyb&iacute; ani titulkovač a koment&aacute;ře.<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"><img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/mBNcv7Pk.jpg" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div><br />\r\nNov&aacute; verze obsahuje &quot;video cache technologii&quot; kterou již zn&aacute;me z jin&yacute;ch programů, ale pod jin&yacute;m n&aacute;zvem. Vytvoř&iacute; se kopie původn&iacute;ch souborů v men&scaron;&iacute; velikosti, takže střih je pak svižněj&scaron;&iacute; a plynulej&scaron;&iacute;. V&scaron;e nav&iacute;c funguje plynule na pozad&iacute;. AVS Video Editor podporuje i využit&iacute; v&yacute;početn&iacute;ho v&yacute;konu grafick&eacute;ho procesu.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nVylep&scaron;eno bylo i prostřed&iacute;, kter&eacute; m&aacute; b&yacute;t intuitivněj&scaron;&iacute; a l&iacute;bivěj&scaron;&iacute;, d&aacute;le obsahuje novou funkci nahr&aacute;v&aacute;n&iacute; obsahu obrazovky a jeden efekt nav&iacute;c - stabilizaci roztřesen&eacute;ho videa.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nProgram AVS Video Editor ve verzi 5.1 je ke stažen&iacute; jako trial verze na webov&yacute;ch str&aacute;nk&aacute;ch v&yacute;robce, plat&iacute; se ne za jeden program, ale za použ&iacute;v&aacute;n&iacute; v&scaron;ech programů v&yacute;robce , buď na jeden rok nebo neomezeně.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"><em>Použit&eacute; zdroje:&nbsp;<a href="http://www.avs4you.com/">http://www.avs4you.com/</a></em></div>\r\n', '8', '35', '1376222685', 430, 'Video, AVS, rezence', '0', 13),
(127, 'Vysokorýchlostný Wi-Fi štandard 802.11ac naberá dych', '211WIFI.png', 'No­vý štan­dard IEEE 802.11ac, kto­rý má umož­niť bez­drô­to­vé Wi-Fi pre­no­sy rých­los­ťou až 1,3 Gb/s, sa ko­neč­ne za­čí­na pre­sa­dzo­vať na tr­hu. Do kon­ca ro­ka by ho ma­lo pod­ľa od­ha­dov ana­ly­ti­kov pod­po­ro­vať už zhru­ba mi­lión pre­da­ných prístrojov...', '<h3 style="color:#aaa; font-style:italic">No&shy;v&yacute; &scaron;tan&shy;dard IEEE 802.11ac, kto&shy;r&yacute; m&aacute; umož&shy;niť bez&shy;dr&ocirc;&shy;to&shy;v&eacute; Wi-Fi pre&shy;no&shy;sy r&yacute;ch&shy;los&shy;ťou až 1,3 Gb/s, sa ko&shy;neč&shy;ne za&shy;č&iacute;&shy;na pre&shy;sa&shy;dzo&shy;vať na tr&shy;hu. Do kon&shy;ca ro&shy;ka by ho ma&shy;lo pod&shy;ľa od&shy;ha&shy;dov ana&shy;ly&shy;ti&shy;kov pod&shy;po&shy;ro&shy;vať už zhru&shy;ba mi&shy;li&oacute;n pre&shy;da&shy;n&yacute;ch pr&iacute;s&shy;tro&shy;jov. V bu&shy;d&uacute;&shy;com ro&shy;ku sa to&shy;to č&iacute;s&shy;lo e&scaron;&shy;te znie&shy;koľ&shy;ko&shy;n&aacute;&shy;so&shy;b&iacute;.</h3>\r\nPod&shy;ľa in&shy;for&shy;m&aacute;&shy;ci&iacute; agen&shy;t&uacute;&shy;ry ABI Re&shy;search za&shy;tiaľ st&aacute;&shy;le tr&shy;hu do&shy;mi&shy;nu&shy;j&uacute; za&shy;ria&shy;de&shy;nia s pod&shy;po&shy;rou &scaron;tan&shy;dar&shy;du 802.11n, kto&shy;r&yacute; pod&shy;po&shy;ru&shy;j&uacute; zhru&shy;ba dve tre&shy;ti&shy;ny v&scaron;et&shy;k&yacute;ch pre&shy;d&aacute;&shy;va&shy;n&yacute;ch pr&iacute;s&shy;tro&shy;jov. U niek&shy;to&shy;r&yacute;ch sa po&shy;tom mož&shy;no stret&shy;n&uacute;ť e&scaron;&shy;te so star&shy;&scaron;&iacute;m &scaron;tan&shy;dar&shy;dom 802.11 b/g (ty&shy;pic&shy;ky ide nap&shy;r&iacute;k&shy;lad o tla&shy;čiar&shy;ne), ale to nič ne&shy;me&shy;n&iacute; na sku&shy;toč&shy;nos&shy;ti, že 802.11ac sa už za&shy;č&iacute;&shy;na v&yacute;&shy;raz&shy;ne pre&shy;sa&shy;dzo&shy;vať v naj&shy;r&ocirc;z&shy;nej&shy;&scaron;om Wi-Fi har&shy;dv&eacute;&shy;ri. Pre&shy;da&shy;je toh&shy;to har&shy;dv&eacute;&shy;ru na&shy;vy&shy;&scaron;e ras&shy;t&uacute; a glo&shy;b&aacute;l&shy;ne do&shy;d&aacute;v&shy;ky Wi-Fi za&shy;ria&shy;de&shy;nia v pr&shy;vom kvar&shy;t&aacute;&shy;li 2013 do&shy;siah&shy;li 43,3 mi&shy;li&oacute;&shy;nov ku&shy;sov, čo je me&shy;dzi&shy;roč&shy;n&yacute; n&aacute;&shy;rast o 16,8 %. Po&shy;diel za&shy;ria&shy;de&shy;n&iacute; s pod&shy;po&shy;rou vy&shy;so&shy;ko&shy;r&yacute;&shy;chlos&shy;tn&eacute;&shy;ho &scaron;tan&shy;dar&shy;du bu&shy;de r&yacute;ch&shy;lo r&aacute;sť a pod&shy;ľa ABI sa do kon&shy;ca ro&shy;ka pre&shy;d&aacute; už spo&shy;m&iacute;&shy;na&shy;n&yacute; mi&shy;li&oacute;n za&shy;ria&shy;de&shy;n&iacute; s pod&shy;po&shy;rou 802.11ac.\r\n\r\n<h3>Roz&shy;die&shy;ly 802.11n a 802.11ac</h3>\r\nPo&shy;dob&shy;ne ako IEEE 802.11n, vy&shy;už&iacute;&shy;va no&shy;v&yacute; &scaron;tan&shy;dard 802.11ac v&yacute;&shy;hod v&auml;č&shy;&scaron;ie&shy;ho poč&shy;tu an&shy;t&eacute;n k vy&shy;tvo&shy;re&shy;niu viac ako jed&shy;n&eacute;&shy;ho d&aacute;&shy;to&shy;v&eacute;&shy;ho pr&uacute;&shy;du &ndash; av&shy;&scaron;ak v pr&iacute;&shy;pa&shy;de 802.11ac m&aacute; byť ten&shy;to d&aacute;&shy;to&shy;v&yacute; pr&uacute;d viac ako troj&shy;n&aacute;&shy;sob&shy;ne r&yacute;ch&shy;lej&shy;&scaron;ie ako u &scaron;tan&shy;dar&shy;du n. Ten&shy;to cieľ mož&shy;no do&shy;siah&shy;nuť za pou&shy;ži&shy;tia p&aacute;s&shy;ma o &scaron;&iacute;r&shy;ke 80 ale&shy;bo 160 MHz, za&shy;tiaľ čo u 802.11n je to maxim&aacute;l&shy;ne 40 MHz. No&shy;v&yacute; &scaron;tan&shy;dard po&shy;tom vy&shy;už&iacute;&shy;va už len frek&shy;ven&shy;ciu 5 GHz a &uacute;pl&shy;ne tak op&uacute;&scaron;&shy;ťa sta&shy;r&eacute; &ldquo;za&shy;&scaron;u&shy;me&shy;n&eacute;&rdquo; p&aacute;s&shy;mo 2,4 GHz, kto&shy;r&eacute; sa vy&shy;už&iacute;&shy;va&shy;lo pri &scaron;tan&shy;dar&shy;doch 802.11b/ga bo&shy;lo vo&shy;li&shy;teľ&shy;n&eacute; aj pre &scaron;tan&shy;dard n.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nĎal&shy;&scaron;ie vy&shy;lep&shy;&scaron;e&shy;nie je spo&shy;je&shy;n&eacute; s vy&shy;uži&shy;t&iacute;m tech&shy;no&shy;l&oacute;&shy;gie for&shy;mo&shy;va&shy;nia vĺn (tzv. beam for&shy;ming), kto&shy;r&aacute; m&aacute; za &uacute;lo&shy;hu sme&shy;ro&shy;vať Wi-Fi sig&shy;n&aacute;l naj&shy;lep&shy;&scaron;ou ces&shy;tou do svoj&shy;ho cie&shy;ľa a m&aacute; tiež za&shy;ru&shy;čiť r&yacute;ch&shy;lej&shy;&scaron;ie d&aacute;&shy;to&shy;v&eacute; pre&shy;no&shy;sy. Niek&shy;to&shy;r&iacute; v&yacute;&shy;rob&shy;co&shy;via t&uacute;&shy;to tech&shy;no&shy;l&oacute;&shy;giu na&shy;sa&shy;di&shy;li už aj u pro&shy;duk&shy;tov za&shy;lo&shy;že&shy;n&yacute;ch na &scaron;tan&shy;dar&shy;de IEEE 802.11n, ale neod&shy;de&shy;li&shy;teľ&shy;nou s&uacute;&shy;čas&shy;ťou je pr&aacute;&shy;ve až u 802.11ac.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSa&shy;moz&shy;rej&shy;me r&yacute;ch&shy;losť 1,3 Gb/s je viac&shy;me&shy;nej teo&shy;re&shy;tic&shy;k&aacute; a mož&shy;no ju do&shy;siah&shy;nuť len v la&shy;bo&shy;ra&shy;t&oacute;r&shy;nych pod&shy;mien&shy;kach, ale aj v praxi sa uka&shy;zu&shy;je, že op&shy;ro&shy;ti 802.11n s&uacute; d&aacute;&shy;to&shy;v&eacute; pre&shy;no&shy;sy v&yacute;&shy;raz&shy;ne r&yacute;ch&shy;lej&shy;&scaron;ie. Av&shy;&scaron;ak je pot&shy;reb&shy;n&eacute; po&shy;č&iacute;&shy;tať aj s t&yacute;m, že do&shy;sah je v tom&shy;to pr&iacute;&shy;pa&shy;de men&shy;&scaron;&iacute; ako u star&shy;&scaron;&iacute;ch &scaron;tan&shy;dar&shy;dov pra&shy;cu&shy;j&uacute;&shy;cich v p&aacute;s&shy;me 2,4 GHz.\r\n<h3>Roz&shy;&scaron;i&shy;ro&shy;va&shy;nie IEEE 802.11ac na tr&shy;hu</h3>\r\nPod&shy;po&shy;ra &scaron;tan&shy;dar&shy;du 802.11ac prav&shy;de&shy;po&shy;dob&shy;ne ne&shy;bu&shy;de pre v&auml;č&shy;&scaron;i&shy;nu ku&shy;pu&shy;j&uacute;&shy;cich z&aacute;&shy;sad&shy;n&yacute;m d&ocirc;&shy;vo&shy;dom k up&shy;gra&shy;du svo&shy;jich exis&shy;tu&shy;j&uacute;&shy;cich za&shy;ria&shy;de&shy;n&iacute;, ale s t&yacute;m, ako bu&shy;de je&shy;ho vy&shy;uži&shy;tie v no&shy;v&yacute;ch pr&iacute;s&shy;tro&shy;joch čo&shy;raz bež&shy;nej&shy;&scaron;ie, sa vďa&shy;ka ich prie&shy;bež&shy;ne ob&shy;me&shy;ne r&yacute;ch&shy;lo roz&shy;&scaron;&iacute;&shy;ri, od&shy;ha&shy;du&shy;j&uacute; ana&shy;ly&shy;ti&shy;ci. V s&uacute;&shy;čas&shy;nos&shy;ti je po&shy;tom čas&shy;tou pre&shy;k&aacute;ž&shy;kou do&shy;siah&shy;nu&shy;tia vy&shy;&scaron;&scaron;ej r&yacute;ch&shy;los&shy;ti sa&shy;mot&shy;n&eacute; pri&shy;po&shy;je&shy;nie k inter&shy;ne&shy;tu (zvl&aacute;&scaron;ť ak je reali&shy;zo&shy;va&shy;n&eacute; pros&shy;tred&shy;n&iacute;c&shy;tvom xDSL tech&shy;no&shy;l&oacute;&shy;gi&iacute;) a r&yacute;ch&shy;le bez&shy;dr&ocirc;&shy;to&shy;v&eacute; pre&shy;no&shy;sy d&aacute;t sa tak t&yacute;&shy;ka&shy;j&uacute; naj&shy;m&auml; inter&shy;nej sie&shy;te v r&aacute;m&shy;ci ur&shy;či&shy;tej lo&shy;ka&shy;li&shy;ty.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nVeľ&shy;k&iacute; hr&aacute;&shy;či na tr&shy;hu už pos&shy;tup&shy;ne vy&shy;ba&shy;vu&shy;j&uacute; no&shy;v&eacute; ge&shy;ne&shy;r&aacute;&shy;cie pr&iacute;s&shy;tro&shy;jov cer&shy;ti&shy;fi&shy;k&aacute;&shy;ciou pre Wi-Fi 802.11ac a je&shy;ho pod&shy;po&shy;ra sa tak sta&shy;ne ne&shy;vyh&shy;nut&shy;nou vlas&shy;tnos&shy;ťou už len z poh&shy;ľa&shy;du nut&shy;nos&shy;ti ne&shy;zaos&shy;t&aacute;&shy;vať za kon&shy;ku&shy;ren&shy;ciou a dr&shy;žať si po&shy;z&iacute;&shy;ciu ino&shy;v&aacute;&shy;to&shy;ra. Hlav&shy;n&yacute;&shy;mi ťa&shy;h&uacute;ň&shy;mi v pre&shy;sa&shy;dzo&shy;va&shy;n&iacute; no&shy;v&eacute;&shy;ho &scaron;tan&shy;dar&shy;du po&shy;tom m&ocirc;&shy;žu byť fir&shy;my D-Link, Net&shy;gear, TP-Link, ZTE, Cis&shy;co, HP ale&shy;bo Aru&shy;ba Networks.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWi-Fi alian&shy;cia, kto&shy;r&aacute; roz&shy;voj &scaron;tan&shy;dar&shy;dov IEEE 802.11 za&shy;stre&shy;&scaron;u&shy;je, na&shy;vy&shy;&scaron;e už od ro&shy;ku 2009 pra&shy;cu&shy;je na ďal&shy;&scaron;ej ge&shy;ne&shy;r&aacute;&shy;cie &scaron;tan&shy;dar&shy;du, ozna&shy;čo&shy;va&shy;nej ako 802.11ad (WiGig). Ten vy&shy;už&iacute;&shy;va ok&shy;rem frek&shy;ven&shy;cie 2,4 GHz (kto&shy;r&aacute; sa op&auml;ť prek&shy;va&shy;pi&shy;vo vra&shy;cia na sc&eacute;&shy;nu) a 5 GHz aj p&aacute;s&shy;mo 60 GHz a mal by vďa&shy;ka to&shy;mu umož&shy;niť do&shy;siah&shy;nu&shy;tie r&yacute;ch&shy;los&shy;ti až 7 Gb/s. Je&shy;ho v&yacute;&shy;voj bol už do&shy;kon&shy;če&shy;n&yacute; a pr&shy;v&eacute; pr&iacute;s&shy;tro&shy;je, kto&shy;r&eacute; bu&shy;d&uacute; pod&shy;po&shy;ro&shy;vať WiGig, by sa na tr&shy;hu ma&shy;li ob&shy;ja&shy;viť za&shy;čiat&shy;kom ro&shy;ka 2014. Na ma&shy;s&iacute;v&shy;ny n&aacute;s&shy;tup si ale bu&shy;d&uacute; mu&shy;sieť e&scaron;&shy;te nie&shy;koľ&shy;ko ro&shy;kov poč&shy;kať.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Zdroj: <a href="http://www.itnews.sk/spravy/technologie/2013-08-12/c158102-vysokorychlostny-wi-fi-standard-802.11ac-nabera-dych" target="_blank">ITNews.sk</a></strong>', '5', '6', '1376305829', 374, 'wifi, vyskokorýchlostná wifi, wifi 802.11ac', '0', 0),
(128, 'GTAV - Ďalšia nádielka screenov a špeciálna prehliadka!', '512gtaV.png', 'Rockstar nám prináša ďalšiu nádielku sreenov ešte pred samotným ohlásením GTA Online a je to naozaj paráda. Myslím, celkom príjemná provokácia od vývojárov z Rockstaru.', 'Pred samotn&yacute;m ohl&aacute;sen&iacute;m GTA Online n&aacute;m v&yacute;voj&aacute;ri z Rockstaru priniesli ďal&scaron;iu n&aacute;dielku screenov! Je to naozaj par&aacute;da! Na obr&aacute;zkoch m&ocirc;žete vidieť lov, reklamy, voľby, podmorsk&eacute; mesto, p&aacute;r z&aacute;berov s lietadlami, a nejak&yacute;mi &quot;ma&scaron;inkami&quot;.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nĎalej V&aacute;s Rockstar poz&yacute;va na <a href="http://www.rockstargames.com/V/" style="color: rgb(39, 174, 96);"><strong>interakt&iacute;vnu prehliadku</strong></a> kde m&ocirc;žete spoznať bliž&scaron;ie Los Santos a Blaine Country, ukazuj&uacute; p&aacute;r vozidiel z hry a možnosti ich ovl&aacute;dania, možnosť investovania do r&ocirc;znych akci&iacute;, už&iacute;vanie marihuany. prekr&aacute;sne v&yacute;hľady, aktu&aacute;lnu volebn&uacute; kampaň, možnosť lietania a n&aacute;kupov. Ďalej priateľsk&yacute;ch susedov a vodn&eacute; &scaron;porty.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://imgs.sector.sk/files/novinky/2013-8-13-18-26-68/GTA-V-image-4960.jpg" style="height:394px; width:700px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://imgs.sector.sk/files/novinky/2013-8-13-18-26-68/GTA-V-image-4415.jpg" style="height:394px; width:700px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://imgs.sector.sk/files/novinky/2013-8-13-18-26-68/GTA-V-image-4533.jpg" style="height:394px; width:700px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://imgs.sector.sk/files/novinky/2013-8-13-18-26-68/GTA-V-image-5604.jpg" style="height:394px; width:700px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://imgs.sector.sk/files/novinky/2013-8-13-18-26-68/GTA-V-image-7491.jpg" style="height:394px; width:700px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" class=