(177, '[JQuery] Načtení obsahu souboru bez obnovení stránky', '5697103.png', 'Jednoduché načítání souborů, bez obnovení stránky, pomocí JQuery.', '<u><strong>1. KROK</strong></u><br />\r\n<br />\r\nDo hlavičky webu přid&aacute;me:\r\n<div class="box">&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;http://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.0.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<u><strong>2. KROK</strong></u><br />\r\n<br />\r\nVytvoř&iacute;me si script, kter&yacute; n&aacute;m bude nač&iacute;tat str&aacute;nky:\r\n<div class="box">&nbsp;$(document).ready(function(){<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$(&#39;#content&#39;).load(&#39;main.html&#39;);<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$(&#39;#menu a&#39;).click(function(){<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;var file = $(this).attr(&#39;href&#39;);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$(&#39;#content&#39;).load(&#39;&#39; + file + &#39;.html&#39;);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;return false;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;});<br />\r\n&nbsp;});</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="background-color:rgb(248, 248, 248); font-family:tahoma; font-size:11px"><span style="color:#000000">$(&#39;#content&#39;).load(&#39;main.html&#39;); </span>- tato č&aacute;st n&aacute;m nač&iacute;t&aacute; str&aacute;nku, kter&aacute; se zobraz&iacute; po prvn&iacute;m načten&iacute; str&aacute;nky v <span style="color:#008000">DIVu</span> s <span style="color:#008000">ID</span> content<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000">$(&#39;#menu a&#39;).click(function(){ </span>// K&oacute;d<span style="color:#000000"> }); </span>- funkce, kter&aacute; se vykon&aacute; po kliknut&iacute; na odkaz v<span style="color:#008000"> </span><span style="color:#008000">DIVu</span> s <span style="color:#008000">ID</span> menu<br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000">var file = $(this).attr(&#39;href&#39;); </span>- do proměnn&eacute; <span style="color:#0000CD">file</span>&nbsp;si ulož&iacute;me obsah tagu <span style="color:#008000">&lt;a&gt;</span> z atributu <span style="color:#008000">href=&quot;&quot;</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#000000">$(&#39;#content</span></span><span style="background-color:rgb(248, 248, 248); font-family:tahoma; font-size:11px"><span style="color:#000000">&#39;).load(&#39;&#39;</span><span style="color:#0000CD"> + file +</span><span style="color:#000000"> &#39;.html&#39;);​ </span>- jako n&aacute;zev souboru&nbsp;načteme obsah proměnn&eacute; <span style="color:#0000FF">file</span> a připoj&iacute;me k tomu koncovku .html (samozřejmě může b&yacute;t i jin&aacute;), obsah souboru se načte do<span style="color:#008000"> DIVu</span> s <span style="color:#008000">ID</span> content<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<u><strong>PŘ&Iacute;KLAD K&Oacute;DU</strong></u></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="box">&lt;head&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&lt;title&gt;JQuery&lt;/title&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;http://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.0.0.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&lt;script&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;$(document).ready(function(){<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$(&#39;#content&#39;).load(&#39;main.html&#39;);<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$(&#39;#menu a&#39;).click(function(){<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;var file = $(this).attr(&#39;href&#39;);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$(&#39;#content&#39;).load(&#39;&#39; + file + &#39;.html&#39;);<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;return false;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;});<br />\r\n&nbsp;});<br />\r\n&nbsp;&lt;/script&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;/head&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;body&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&lt;div id=&quot;menu&quot;&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;help&quot;&gt;Help&lt;/a&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;login&quot;&gt;Login&lt;/a&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&lt;div id=&quot;content&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;/body&gt;</div>\r\n<span style="font-size:12px">Při načten&iacute; str&aacute;nky se n&aacute;m zobraz&iacute; obsah souboru&nbsp;<span style="color:#000000">main.html</span>, kter&yacute; se mus&iacute; nach&aacute;zet ve stejn&eacute;m adres&aacute;ři jako soubor s t&iacute;mto k&oacute;dem.<br />\r\nPo kliknut&iacute; na odkaz&nbsp;​<span style="color:#000000"><span style="background-color:rgb(248, 248, 248); font-family:tahoma">&lt;a href=&quot;help&quot;&gt;Help</span><span style="background-color:rgb(248, 248, 248); font-family:tahoma">&lt;/a&gt; </span></span><span style="background-color:rgb(248, 248, 248); font-family:tahoma">se n&aacute;m načte obsah souboru&nbsp;<span style="color:#000000">help.html</span>, kter&yacute; se mus&iacute; nach&aacute;zet ve stejn&eacute;m adres&aacute;ři jako soubor s t&iacute;mto k&oacute;dem.</span></span>', '15', '3', '1382781615', 922, 'JQuery, load, web', '0', 0),
