(185, 'OpenType a TrueType fonty', '9577506.jpg', 'Fonty sú rozdelené do kategórie OpenType a TrueType. V dnešnom článku si vysvetlíme tieto pojmy.', 'Fonty s&uacute; rozdelen&eacute; do kateg&oacute;rie OpenType a TrueType. V dne&scaron;nom čl&aacute;nku si ich charakterizujeme a zhrnieme.\r\n<h3><strong><img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://blog.iconspedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/10/evolution_true_type_font.jpg" style="height:585px; width:400px" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nTrueType Format</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>TrueType Fromat</strong> je &scaron;tandard pre popis vektorov&yacute;ch poč&iacute;tačov&yacute;ch p&iacute;smen - fontov, vyvinut&yacute; koncom 80. rokov spoločnosťou Apple ako konkurent Adobe Type 1, ktor&eacute; sa použ&iacute;vali v jazyku PostScript.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Podpora <strong>TrueType</strong> je dnes implementovan&aacute; v <strong>OS MS Windows a GNU/Linux</strong>.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nP&iacute;sma <strong>TrueType</strong> v OS Windows maj&uacute; pr&iacute;ponu TTF.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJeho n&aacute;stupcom je OpenType, ktor&yacute; v sebe spojuje to najlep&scaron;ie z TrueType a konkurenčn&eacute;ho &scaron;tandardu PostScript Type 1 a m&aacute; oveľa lep&scaron;ie rie&scaron;en&eacute; probl&eacute;my s lokaliz&aacute;ciou p&iacute;smen.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong><img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://www.designbypxlgirl.com/insights/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/dbp_blog_img-typo_sourcecode-sans.jpg" style="height:375px; width:560px" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nOpenType Format</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>OpenType</strong>&nbsp;je &scaron;tandard pre popis vektorov&yacute;ch poč&iacute;tačov&yacute;ch p&iacute;smen&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;fontov, vyvinut&yacute; spoločnosťou&nbsp;Microsoft&nbsp;ako n&aacute;stupca &scaron;tandardu&nbsp;<strong>TrueType</strong>. Nesk&ocirc;r sa k pr&aacute;ci na &scaron;tandarde&nbsp;pripojil i najv&auml;č&scaron;&iacute;&nbsp;rival &ndash; spoločnosť&nbsp;<strong>Adobe Systems</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Podpora <strong>OpenType</strong> je dnes implementovan&aacute;&nbsp;v operačn&yacute;ch syst&eacute;moch&nbsp;<strong>Microsoft Windows,&nbsp;Mac OS X&nbsp;a&nbsp;Linux.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>P&iacute;sma <strong>OpenType</strong> v operačnom&nbsp;syst&eacute;me&nbsp;Windows maj&uacute;&nbsp;v&auml;č&scaron;inou pr&iacute;ponu <strong>OTF</strong>, i keď&nbsp;sa&nbsp;použ&iacute;va&nbsp;aj&nbsp;star&scaron;&iacute; pr&iacute;pona <strong>TTF</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hlavn&eacute;&nbsp;v&yacute;hody oproti star&scaron;&iacute;m &scaron;tandardom:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>znaky m&ocirc;žu byť&nbsp;pop&iacute;san&eacute;&nbsp;pomocou&nbsp;zvyklosti&nbsp;TrueType&nbsp;alebo&nbsp;PostScript</li>\r\n	<li>je založen&yacute; na Unicode, z čoho&nbsp;vypl&yacute;va&nbsp;menej&nbsp;probl&eacute;mov&nbsp;s lokaliz&aacute;ciou&nbsp;p&iacute;siem&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>jeden s&uacute;bor&nbsp;m&ocirc;že popisovať&nbsp;až 65 536 znakov</li>\r\n	<li>je bez probl&eacute;mov&nbsp;prenosn&yacute;&nbsp;medzi syst&eacute;mami&nbsp;<strong>Windows,&nbsp;Apple&nbsp;a&nbsp;Unix</strong></li>\r\n	<li>m&aacute; lep&scaron;iu&nbsp;podporu pre&nbsp;typografick&eacute; &scaron;peciality ako s&uacute;&nbsp;zliatky&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;ligat&uacute;ry</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<em>Zdroj:&nbsp;<a href="http://cs.wikipedia.org/">http://cs.wikipedia.org</a></em></p>\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;', '9', '6', '1383575446', 752, 'grafika, fonty, rozdiel, medzi, open, type, true, type', '0', 0),
(186, 'Humble Bundle - zaplať koľko chceš a pomôž charite!', '3468269.jpg', 'Humble WB Games Bundle & Humble Weekly Sale: Team 17 - peckové hry už od 1 USD.', '<p>Ak ste e&scaron;te o Humble Bundle nepočuli m&ocirc;žete ľutovať. Ide o bal&iacute;ček hier, za ktor&eacute; m&ocirc;žete zaplatiť sumu, ktor&uacute; si sami zvol&iacute;te. Ďalej si m&ocirc;žete vybrať kam peniaze poputuj&uacute;, či pre v&yacute;voj&aacute;rov hier, na charitu alebo pre zakladateľov Humble Bundle. To koľko zaplat&iacute;te je len na v&aacute;s, no ak zaplat&iacute;te viac ako je priemer (alebo stanoven&aacute; pevn&aacute; suma) m&ocirc;žete z&iacute;skať aj ďal&scaron;ie bonusov&eacute; hry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Moment&aacute;lne* s&uacute; na str&aacute;nke <a href="https://www.humblebundle.com/">humblebundle.com</a> dostupn&eacute; dve predajn&eacute; akcie.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" src="http://i.imgur.com/4sEYa7d.png" style="height:98px; width:487px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Prv&aacute; <em>The Humble WB Games Bundle</em> trv&aacute; e&scaron;te do utorka 19.11.2013. V nej napr&iacute;klad za <strong>1 USD</strong> (v prepočte 0,74&euro;**) m&ocirc;žete z&iacute;skať &scaron;tyri hry <em>Batman: Arkham Asylum GOTY</em>, <em>F.E.A.R. 2: Project Origin</em>, <em>F.E.A.R. 3</em> a <em>Lord of the Rings: War in the North</em>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" src="http://i.imgur.com/IF0FQcb.png" style="height:202px; width:525px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ak budete ochotn&yacute; zaplatiť viac ako <strong>priemer</strong>, ktor&yacute; je moment&aacute;lne 4,62 USD* (v prepočte 3,42&euro;**) z&iacute;skate ďal&scaron;ie dve hry <em>Scribblenauts Unlimited</em> a <em>Batman: Arkham City GOTY</em>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" src="http://i.imgur.com/dPmVXCk.png" style="height:205px; width:267px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" src="http://i.imgur.com/KBFLIV0.png" style="height:125px; width:710px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Druh&aacu