(230, 'Predstavenie grafikov #1 - Matúš Bence', '784matusbence.png', 'V tomto článku by som Vám chcel priblížiť slovenského kvalitného grafika Matúša Bence, ktorý tvoril práce pre mnohé známe slovenské spoločnosti ako Tatra Banka, Zlatý Bažant, Šariš, O2 či iné.', '<p>Vitajte v prvom čl&aacute;nku zo s&eacute;rie &quot;<em>Prestavenie grafikov</em>&quot;, v ktorom si nap&iacute;&scaron;eme niečo o grafikovi <strong>Mat&uacute;&scaron; Bence</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Na tohto človeka som narazil čistou n&aacute;hodou, keď som si prezeral pr&aacute;ce na Design in Europe a zap&aacute;čila sa mi jedna pr&aacute;ca, tak som si pozrel portf&oacute;lio, kde toho bolo viac.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="boximg"><img alt="" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/6MwdN27b.jpg" style="width: 100%" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>T&iacute;m <a href="http://matusbence.com"><strong>MATUSBENCE.COM</strong></a> tvoria traja ľudia, a to Mat&uacute;&scaron; Bence ako vizu&aacute;lny riaditeľ a fotograf, ďalej Vanda Belakov&aacute;, ktor&aacute; zast&aacute;va v t&iacute;me sk&ocirc;r manaž&eacute;rsku funkciu a nakoniec Luk&aacute;&scaron; Hajka ako 3D grafik a CGI ved&uacute;ci.</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><em><span style="font-size:20px;">Sme mal&aacute; skupina mlad&yacute;ch profesion&aacute;lov založen&aacute; Mat&uacute;&scaron;om Bence, kto je z&aacute;roveň l&iacute;drom v&scaron;etk&yacute;ch projektov v &uacute;lohe vizu&aacute;lneho režis&eacute;ra a fotografa.</span></em></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="sk"><span class="hps">Skupina poskytuje</span> <span class="hps">komplexn&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">vizu&aacute;lne</span> <span class="hps">rie&scaron;enie</span> <span class="hps">-</span> <span class="hps">vr&aacute;tane</span> <span class="hps">vizu&aacute;lneho</span> <span class="hps">poňatie</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">predv&yacute;robnej</span> <span class="hps">konzult&aacute;cie</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">technickej</span> <span class="hps">podpory</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">v&yacute;roby</span> <span class="hps">fotografi&iacute;</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps">postprodukcia</span> <span class="hps">a</span> <span class="hps">retu&scaron;e</span> <span class="hps">a</span> <span class="hps">pokročil&eacute;</span> <span class="hps">3D</span> <span class="hps">CGI</span><span>.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div class="boximg"><img alt="" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/x2TFtchp.jpg" style="width: 100%" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="boximg"><img alt="" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/LB8T9mRH.jpg" style="width: 100%" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="boximg"><img alt="" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/6T37YnRv.jpg" style="width: 100%" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="boximg"><img alt="" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/mY3hyXLR.jpg" style="width: 100%" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="boximg"><img alt="" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/jyK7GxRQ.jpg" style="width: 100%" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="boximg"><img alt="" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/BpXVtGNq.jpg" style="width: 100%" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="boximg"><img alt="" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/cZ8Y7xpz.jpg" style="width: 100%" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="boximg"><img alt="" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/MVJPN4zY.jpg" style="width: 100%" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong><span style="font-size:16px;">Inform&aacute;cie &amp; odkazy:</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Krajina p&ocirc;vodu: Slovensk&aacute; republika<br />\r\nPortf&oacute;lio: <a href="http://matusbence.com">matusbence.com</a><br />\r\nFacebook: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/MatusBencecom/223291601036411">https://www.facebook.com/pages/MatusBencecom/223291601036411</a><br />\r\nTwitter: <a href="https://twitter.com/MatusBence">https://twitter.com/MatusBence</a><br />\r\nLinkedIn: <a href="http://www.linkedin.com/pub/matus-bence/40/71/426">http://www.linkedin.com/pub/matus-bence/40/71/426</a><br />\r\nTumblr: <a href="http://matusbence.tumblr.com/">http://matusbence.tumblr.com/</a><br />\r\nInstagram: <a href="http://instagram.com/matusbence">http://instagram.com/matusbence</a></p>\r\n', '22', '1', '1396692483', 1027, 'predstavenie, grafikov, 1, matus, bence, fotograf', '0', 7),
(231, 'CG - VFX Breakdowns #1', '39783182.png', 'Zopár zaujmavých videí, pre tých ktorých zaujmajú špeciálne efekty, alebo pohyblivá grafika určite sa pozrite.', 'Na &uacute;vod by som r&aacute;d začal moj&iacute;m najobľ&uacute;benej&scaron;&iacute;m breakdownom, Knife film.<br />\r\nPri tvorbe boli použit&eacute; tieto porgramy: Cinema 4D R14, Adobe After Effects cs6,<br />\r\nPluginy - Videocopilot 3D Element, Optical flares, Red Giant Trapcode suite.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/2FWM1ZvPybM?rel=0" width="560"></iframe><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRealistick&eacute; 3D spracovanie simul&aacute;cie vody a prostredia od &scaron;t&uacute;dia Looking Pirates skratka LP.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/8jD1bz4N3_0?rel=0" width="560"></iframe><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLamborgini aventador spot, vo videu si m&ocirc;žete v&scaron;imn&uacute;ť n&aacute;dhern&yacute; matte painting.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/d1xbB4Ys2Wk?rel=0" width="560"></iframe><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBreakdown na film &quot;Stalingrad&quot; od &scaron;t&uacute;dia MainRoadPost ktor&eacute; sa zaober&aacute; tvorbou &scaron;peci&aacute;lnich efektov,<br />\r\npracovali na filme Wanted, a ďal&scaron;ie ...<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/rwzwxGB2NbU?rel=0" width="560"></iframe><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNa z&aacute;ver<br />\r\nzaujmav&aacute; reklama na chladničku :)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/eMxZIKtY_mE?rel=0" width="560"></iframe><br />\r\n&nbsp;', '13', '82', '1396700875', 633, 'CG, VFX, Breakdown, visual effects', '0', 6),
(233, 'Video: Fotografie z textu', '954michael_jackson_by_zeelina-d63ylog.png', 'Připravili jsme si pro Vás další tutoriál z pohledu videa na sekci GIMP. Tentokrát si ukážeme, jak vytvořit jednoduše textovou fotografii.', '<div>Dne&scaron;n&iacute; čl&aacute;nek bude opět ve stylu videa. V tomto videu si uk&aacute;žeme, jak si jednodu&scaron;e můžeme udělat z obyčejn&eacute; fotografie textovou fotografii. Pokud tedy m&aacute;te program GIMP a chtěli by jste si vyzkou&scaron;et něco nov&eacute;ho, tak nev&aacute;hejte a zkou&scaron;ejte. Douf&aacute;m, že se V&aacute;m tutori&aacute;l bude l&iacute;bit a budeme m&iacute;t nějakou odezvu, abychom věděli, že tuto pr&aacute;ci neděl&aacute;me zbytečně :)</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<iframe allowfullscreen="" class="boximg" frameborder="0" height="315" scrolling="no" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/8lIL_RuFGy8?rel=0" width="500"></iframe><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" class="boximg" src="http://data.icrazy.eu/i/wB67FG42.png" style="height: 548px; width: 500px;" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n', '17', '35', '1397981181', 680, 'Video, návod, tutorial, gimp, fotografie, z, textu', '0', 0),
